<P>
 -- Joe Carter is on pace to drive in 208 runs this season, but the ball is not 
juiced. Pass it on. 
</P>
<P>
 -- Kenny Lofton has already hit six home runs this season, but the ball is not 
juiced. 
</P>
<P>
 -- OK, we had better stop there. 
