 -- In other news, Scott Erickson pitched a no-hitter for the Minnesota Twins 
this month. Really, that's what it says. Can we get a fact-checker on this? 
</P>
<P>
 -- What's in a name? Just ask the St. Louis Cardinals, who tried replacing Lee 
Smith with Willie Smith. 
