</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA052394-0199 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 044579 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 23, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Life & Style; Part E; Page 1; Column 1; View Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
